Method Detail

preparePriors

protected void preparePriors()
Hack the prior probabilities using the number of clusters per training label. TacoaDistanceMeasure takes the prior to be per label, not per cluster. So, the "distance" between a sample and a cluster depends on how many clusters share the same training label.
